    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You’ve mastered several of the Fool’s Errand discipline’s secret techniques.</em></p><p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Fool’s Errand Style, Fool’s Errand Scholar, Climb 11 ranks.</p><p><strong>Benefit</strong>: You gain access to the following two special actions in combat.</p><p>Combo Breaker (Ex): You can expend a readied boost as an immediate action when you are hit with and take damage from with a melee or ranged attack. Make an attack roll with a weapon you are wielding. Further attack rolls by your opponent (including touch attacks) during this turn are rolled against your attack roll’s result, rather than your AC.</p><p>Rising Dragon Fist (Ex): You can expend a readied counter as a swift action while prone to stand up and cause one adjacent creature to become flat-footed against your next attack against them this turn.</p>",
